--------------------------
Modification of data
--------------------
open a file in notepad and edit it.
git status
git add .
git commit -m "sample data"
git status
git push

=============
deleting a file
-------------
ls
rm file1
ls
git status
git add .
git commit -m "sample file deleted"
git push

